Package: beaconstools
Title: Building, Evaluating and Ranking Ecological Benchmarks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Marc", "Edwards", , "me1@uablerta.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0800-8002"))
Description: This package impliments the BEACONs toolbox in R. Ecological Benchmarks are built by calling the BUILDER software. Benchmarks can then be ranked based on their ecological representation relative to a reference area, and based on a range of other ranking metrics.
